dict_0487 = {
    '"New Magincia"': '"新馬金西亞"',
    '"Robin", "Leavell"': '"Robin", "Leavell"',
    '"The man before you examines you with shifty eyes. He has a slightly crouched posture as if constantly poised to strike out at the world around him."': '眼前的男人用狡詐的眼神打量著你。他微微弓著身子，彷彿隨時準備對周圍的世界發動攻擊。',
    '"\"A living that would not have been anything near as profitable if not for thy good works, Battles.\"*"': '"「要不是你的出色表現，Battles，這份營生可賺不了那麼多錢。」*"',
    '"\"Battles. M\'self, I be a stranger to New Magincia.\""': '"「Battles。我自己對新馬金西亞來說也是個陌生人。」"',
    '"\"Be seein\' ye.\"*"': '"「回頭見。」*"',
    '"\"Canst thou imagine spending thine entire life here with nothing happening day after day after day? \'Tis enough to drive a man mad!\""': '"「你能想像在這裡度過餘生，日復一日什麼事都沒發生嗎？這足以把人逼瘋！」"',
    '"\"Gamblin\' is how Robin makes his living. I do not think he has had a regular post in all of his life!\""': '"「Robin 靠賭博維生。我不認為他這輩子有過一份正當工作！」"',
    '"\"Har! Har! Har! Har!\""': '"「哈！哈！哈！哈！」"',
    '"\"He\'s a lady\'s man, he is. But do not be thinkin\' he cannot handle hissel\' inna fight. T\'would be yer last mistake.\""': '"「他是個萬人迷，沒錯。但別以為他不會打架。那會是你最後一個錯誤。」"',
    '"\"I be hired as a bodyguard for Master Robin, as is me partner, Leavell. The pay be good.\""': '"「我受雇做 Robin 少爺的保鏢，我的夥伴 Leavell 也是。報酬很不錯。」"',
    '"\"I can near out wrestle thee, Battles, ye old dog!\"*"': '"「我幾乎能把你摔倒， Battles ，你這老狗！」*"',
    '"\"I sar a locket jus\' like the one thou be describin\' in the possession o\' Master Robin. The last time I sar it was... Lessee... It was right before the three of us went drinkin\' at the Modest Damsel.\""': '"「我看過一個就像你描述的小金匣在 Robin 少爺手裡。我最後一次看到它是在……讓我想想……就在我們三個去謙遜少女喝酒之前。」"',
    '"\"Just the practice Leavell has had in fending off jealous husbands \'twould make any man a master combatant!\""': '"「光是 Leavell 抵擋嫉妒的丈夫們的練習，就足以讓任何人成為戰鬥大師了！」"',
    '"\"Robin be a high stakes gamblin\' gent who makes his living inna casino at Buccaneer\'s Den.\""': '"「Robin 是一個玩高賠率賭博的紳士，在海盜巢穴的賭場裡謀生。」"',
    '"\"So many!\"*"': '"「這麼多！」*"',
    '"\"Strangers? ~~Thou must mean us!\" Battles snorts loudly."': '"「陌生人？~~你一定是在說我們！」Battles 大聲哼著氣。"',
    '"\"Thank yer, Milord.\"*"': '"「謝謝你，大人。」*"',
    '"\"The casino in Buccaneer\'s Den is called the House of Games and it the most fabulous place I have ever seen in me life. I shall never forget the first time Robin took me there. He walked away with a hundred gold pieces for less than an hour\'s work!\""': '"「海盜巢穴的賭場叫做遊戲屋，那是我這輩子見過最棒的地方。我永遠不會忘記 Robin 第一次帶我去那裡。他不到一個小時就贏走了一百枚金幣！」"',
    '"\"The people here are so lacking in education that they never even heard of gamblin\' before! Never heard of gamblin\'? That is what life is all about!\""': '"「這裡的人太缺乏教育了，他們以前甚至沒聽說過賭博！沒聽過賭博？那才是人生的意義啊！」"',
    '"\"We be looking to get off this boring rock, New Magincia, and back to Buccaneer\'s Den. If ye have a way to get us there, and away from these peasant knaves, Master Robin shall pay ye well.\""': '"「我們正想離開這個無聊的石頭島，新馬金西亞，回到海盜巢穴。如果你有辦法帶我們去那裡，遠離這些鄉巴佬， Robin 少爺會付你豐厚的報酬。」"',
    '"\"What?\" asks Battles."': '"「什麼？」Battles 問。"',
    '"\"Why, I reckon Leavell has broken near as many hearts as I have made stop beating!\""': '"「哎呀，我估計 Leavell 傷過的心，幾乎和我讓停止跳動的心臟一樣多！」"',
    '"\"Why, I thank thee for the compliment, Battles!\"*"': '"「哎呀，謝謝你的讚美， Battles ！」*"',
    '"boring rock", "peasant knaves"': '"無聊的石頭島", "鄉巴佬"',
    '"gamblin\' gent", "casino"': '"賭博紳士", "賭場"',
    '"lady\'s man", "fight"': '"萬人迷", "打架"',
    '"locket"': '"小金匣"',
    '"name", "job", "bye"': '"姓名", "職業", "告辭"',
    '"strangers"': '"陌生人"'
}

